<section class="how-it-works-3d" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="hiw-intro">
    <h2 class="section-title">How SATrack Works Under the Hood</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Scroll down to see how your words travel through our AI pipeline — from raw text to intelligent retrieval.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hiw-sticky">
    <canvas id="hiw-canvas"></canvas>
    <div class="hiw-labels">
      <div class="hiw-stage" data-stage="0">
        <div class="hiw-stage-num">1</div>
        <h3>You type a word</h3>
        <p>Your query enters as raw text — just a string of characters like <strong>"perspicacious"</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw-stage" data-stage="1">
        <div class="hiw-stage-num">2</div>
        <h3>Tokens become vectors</h3>
        <p>Our embedding model converts your word into a <strong>1024-dimensional vector</strong> — a precise numerical fingerprint that captures its meaning</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw-stage" data-stage="2">
        <div class="hiw-stage-num">3</div>
        <h3>Stored in a vector database</h3>
        <p>Every word in our database lives in a high-dimensional space. <strong>pgvector</strong> indexes them all for instant cosine-similarity search</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw-stage" data-stage="3">
        <div class="hiw-stage-num">4</div>
        <h3>Retrieved by similarity</h3>
        <p>Your query vector finds its nearest neighbors — the most <strong>semantically similar entries</strong> surface automatically</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw-stage" data-stage="4">
        <div class="hiw-stage-num">5</div>
        <h3>AI generates your entry</h3>
        <p>Retrieved examples are fed into the LLM as <strong>few-shot context</strong>, producing mnemonics and stories that match real quality standards</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hiw-progress-track">
      <div class="hiw-progress-fill" id="hiw-progress-fill"></div>
      <div class="hiw-progress-labels">
        <span>Input</span>
        <span>Tokenize</span>
        <span>Embed</span>
        <span>Store</span>
        <span>Retrieve</span>
        <span>Augment</span>
        <span>Generate</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

